column5: Mine had its embarrassing moments!  I was in a Starbucks Coffee today when my stomach started rumbling and I realized that I desperately needed to pass gas. The place was packed but the music was really loud so to get relief and reduce embarrassment I timed my releases to the beat of the music. After a couple of songs I started to feel much better. I finished my coffee and noticed that everyone was staring at me.
Awesome!! Were you at least able to match the bass beat for beat?
Freaking hilarious!  So I take it you peed off a lot people!
